                "invention-title": [
                    "Ultrafine tungsten powder preparation method with low energy consumption",
                    "一种低能耗的超细钨粉制备方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention relates to the technical field of tungsten processing, and discloses a low-energy-consumption superfine tungsten powder preparation method which comprises the following steps: S1, in a down-hydrogen reduction stage, tungsten oxide is fed into an outer furnace tube from the furnace end of a rotary furnace, the outer furnace tube inclines downwards and rotates, dry hydrogen is continuously introduced from the furnace end, and the flowing directions of the hydrogen and the tungsten oxide are controlled to be the same; s2, a reverse hydrogen reduction stage: a tungsten intermediate product generated by the reaction in the cis-hydrogen stage passes through a cis-reverse hydrogen convergence point and then is led to a high-temperature reduction zone of the rotary furnace, and the flow directions of hydrogen and the tungsten intermediate product are controlled to be opposite in the process; the tungsten intermediate product is subjected to a reduction reaction in a high-temperature reduction area in a partitioned gradient heating mode, and tungsten powder is formed; s3, reverse hydrogen cooling stage: conveying the tungsten powder to a cooling area of the rotary furnace, introducing dry hydrogen from the tail end of the rotary furnace, and controlling the flowing directions of the hydrogen and the tungsten powder to be opposite; and S4, a post-treatment stage: discharging the cooled tungsten powder out of the rotary furnace, and sieving and passivating to obtain the superfine tungsten powder. According to the high-dispersion and low-energy-consumption superfine tungsten powder preparation method, the high-quality and stable-quality superfine tungsten powder can be prepared, the productivity advantage can be brought into full play, the energy consumption cost can be reduced, the production problem existing in existing industrial superfine tungsten powder preparation is effectively solved, and the method is suitable for industrial production of the superfine tungsten powder. And efficient utilization of tungsten resources, energy conservation, reasonable cost control and the like are promoted."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明涉及钨加工技术领域，公开了一种低能耗的超细钨粉制备方法，包括如下步骤：S1顺氢还原阶段：将氧化钨从回转炉的炉头端送入至外炉管中，外炉管向下倾斜、并转动，另从炉头端持续通入干燥氢气，控制氢气与氧化钨的流动方向相同；S2逆氢还原阶段：顺氢阶段反应产生的钨中间产物经过顺逆氢汇合点后，通向回转炉的高温还原区，此过程控制氢气与钨中间产物的流动方向相反；钨中间产物在高温还原区，采用分区梯度加热的方式，进行还原反应，形成钨粉；S3逆氢冷却阶段：将钨粉输送至回转炉的冷却区，从回转炉的炉尾端通入干燥氢气，控制氢气与钨粉的流动方向相反；S4后处理阶段：将冷却后的钨粉，排出回转炉，经过过筛、钝化，得到超细钨粉。本发明提供的高分散、低能耗的超细钨粉制备方法，既能实现制备高质量且质量稳定的超细钨粉，又能充分发挥出产能优势，且可降低能源消耗的成本，有效解决现有的工业制超细钨粉中存在的生产问题，促进钨资源的高效利用、能源的节约、成本的合理控制等。"
                }
